title: Reptile-ownership : household penetration rates 2007 to 2013
summary: In general Penetration rates has fallen over the Year.
Penetration rates is slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2009, and lastly roughly constant from 2009 to 2011.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
The highest Penetration rates, of value 2.1 was reached at Year 2008
The lowest Penetration rates, of value 1.5 was reported at Year 2009
